Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:18.26,op_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}aoi kuni no miru story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:22.01,op_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}kagayaku hitomi
