Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:15.11,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Dawn comes softer than a sleeping breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:23.16,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,0)}Your dream runs through the forest now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:30.17,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,200)}You wake up and stir to find the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.93,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If you've lost it, I'll find it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:47.50,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}It's hidden in our future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:55.98,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Now if we joined hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:03.41,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}we would go far away without letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:11.46,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In the memory of a far off day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:18.26,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}the story of the blue country bloomed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:22.01,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Shining eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:26.19,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}Your singing voice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.97,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,200)}Let's share it
