Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:06.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and Careless Negotiations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:48.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have left you alone till dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:54.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fun for me as a trader!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I know you wouldn't accept that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:12.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's narrow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too narrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I won't deny that it's inconvenient,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:20.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I like this kind of messy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}It has a certain weight to it from the years it's been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:30.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how a tool slowly changes shape over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:33.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,after being used for a long time it becomes unrivaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how the shape of a river changes with time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't really understand your analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a person's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You call it "soul" or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Soul", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:56.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could pull it out and look at it, that might be a good analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:02.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly being chipped away at, injured, and repaired,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the point where one could look at it and say, "This is mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me your hand, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:16.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:24.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If your soul could be pulled out and looked at...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it would be dyed in my color.{'covered' because 'stained' has too negative a connotation in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:36.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be more appropriate to say "poisoned".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be a deadly poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've completely fallen for this smile, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what color is your soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What color?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Various colors, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sense a selfish, possessive desire from me, right?{please do something about the phrase monopolistic desire lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we see a fork in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you deal with such a selfish possessive desire?{ again}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for such difficult problems I could never solve...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:36.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not rare for there to be others who easily understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:42.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're suffering from jealousy that arises from such possessive desires?{ maybe dominatrix fits! lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you're seeking a means to deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I said yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it from your perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can come up with the best answer immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is that such feelings are impossible to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But self-hatred will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:09.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, right, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessiveness and self-hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:25.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you just tried to step into my shoes and figure out my inner desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:30.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you just thought up how you want me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Males really are idiotic creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're attracted by females being jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:42.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,acting all distressed and meek while wanting you and hating themselves, right?{ probably still needs some rephrasing lol.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:47.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you want them to cling to the hand you kindly offer them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:01.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking just to tease you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know how many I've had?{ better expression募集中}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:15.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized again just how delicate my heart is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:23.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's a difficult person, so let's do this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The pleasant, whimsical banter with you ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess I'm back to boring reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about going back to the inn to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:40.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't be sheep I'd be counting on top of the bed.{ rofl.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:41.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:52.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I really am a fool, even amongst men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was introduced by Abe Boland.{ check name}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's certainly a pleasing reaction to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Rigolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:14.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put all your effort into it, it's possible to keep them green all year.{ I hear いちれんじゅう but I can only make sense of it as 一年中}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about you from Fruhl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said there was someone with a strange request for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lawrence. Ah, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Rigolo Deidre. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my traveling companion—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:48.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite happy that you were awed by my prized garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:51.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I give you in thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:55.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you heard from Abe Boland,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:09:01.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was hoping you could show me the records regarding old legends and such in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:06.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that really was what you came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:06.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fruhl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Abe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she puts on such a hard face, she's too playful.{ I just spent ages on this line because I misheard ちゃめっけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:19.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're not a long-bearded, frowning, difficult person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's saying all sorts of things about me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:28.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it's not a complete lie that I'm a difficult person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, recently I've been refusing meetings with people as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a merchant from outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for us to be talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you came at a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be what they call god's guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting was still going on not long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it finally wrapped up and ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:58.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As one might expect of a merchant who was introduced by that stubborn girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:06.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Always using one's utmost wit and cunning can become quite confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The back of the back is the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:13.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, you thought to yourself, \N"Ah, the meeting ended early." right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:19.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the scribe for the Fifty-man meeting, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:22.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand the changing expressions of many people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't understand just by your expressions, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:30.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth starts to show when combined with the movements of your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just an act of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had ill intentions, I wouldn't reveal what I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I could understand what someone really thinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good at communicating what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me a failure as a merchant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I'm not too popular with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All the old books are in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the back of the back is the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he was looking at my face too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've seen such a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it's true he has no ill intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:27.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But with someone with such a skill by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you could probably lead a very relaxed, worry-free life.{ maybe this would sound better making it more direct with 'I' rather than 'one'}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always brimming with ill intentions, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:46.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold back my curiosity, so if you don't mind my asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,why do you want to know the legends of hundreds of years ago? {  I would drop the "Just" at the start. }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:58.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's searching for her own origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her origins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:05.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to various circumstances, I'm guiding her on her way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going north.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the exact location yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the stage where we're trying to find it using a legend she remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure you have your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:32.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes children that come down from the north stay in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:38.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing better than returning safely to one's homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:49.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is everything, so I thought it might be best if you take them all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop those, it'll be three days without food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I'd like to ask you to read them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:07.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I trust Fruhl, so if she trusts you I'll trust you too.{ think I need to use the word trust a few more times?} {  Friends of Kamina? }{But I believe in Fruhl, so I believes in you, whom Fruhl belives in  :o} {PIERCE THE HEAVENS WITH YOUR DORIRUUUUU}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, others may not think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll be careful.{ am I guessing too much by context here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:22.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be really easy to wave your hands like that when you're not holding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:26.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch your mouth doesn't get you jilted one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Males just get overexcited when flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm in no position to, I just get frustrated.{ noooo, another pun! 立つ瀬がないのに、腹ばかり立つな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even being gluttonous has its limits, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's a nice evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, if we had nothing but nights like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet and salty water, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet and salty water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The master will glare at you if you go out to other inns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it'd be a problem if we went every night. {literal.. needs fixing}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you drink much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking with a fur trader from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:13.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, there's little snow this year, so heading up there is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for going out of your way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:20.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know more details, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Korka Coose. {コルカ・クース ... except corka is a girl's name. not sure what to do with this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's staying on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He mentioned that he's normally free during evenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want more info, go ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:45.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the time being, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:20.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything that scares you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going well at the moment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not caught up in any difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the road north this year seems straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:50.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't gotten into any fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm afraid of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:13.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm afraid of is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:15.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The end of our journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:23.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that's also scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something more scary than that. {she knows he's gonna bone her when she's sleeping}{ sure she's not scared he WON'T bone her? xD}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:38.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you come to realize what it is, I might be a bit troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you go downstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but only to the point where I don't get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:52.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I like possessive girls who hate themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a witch sneeze or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did time stop? { ZA WARUDO }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm a merchant but the old man isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I met with Rigolo without issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has such a gloomy face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's depressing being around someone so dreary. {10 bucks says someone misses the blinking SARCASM lights}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious of that special skill of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rigolo took a liking to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:34.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to partner with him, most other merchants would be defenseless against you, don't you think?{あれと組んで商売したら、ほとんどの商人は丸裸も同然だと思わないか yeah... no idea}{ had a go}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately he didn't seem to have that intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His joy in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:44.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,is taking repose in that dilapidated mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the garden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:54.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very rare to see glass windows that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:06.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they came to a conclusion at the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately I didn't get to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you manage to get that out of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is wary around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:31.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, if we could hear whether it's true or not from his own mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly it may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what interests me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:43.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,what your objective is in pursuing this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight to the point, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come here for small business deals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or some trivial bargaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for some way to make a large profit from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What else is there besides that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoiding a huge loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People have two eyes, but it's hard to watch out for both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:18.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right in that avoiding a huge loss is a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:19.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trading in stone statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the Holy Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:34.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just dragging stones, so the profit margins aren't great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:39.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment the church offers its prayers to them, I can sell them at a high price. {uhhh... definitely not right lol  これに教会が祈りを捧げた途端}{ fixed a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:44.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the Northern Expedition each year, there are a ridiculous number of people who buy them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be thankful for religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:54.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately I don't pocket the profit from the blessing, but I make up for it in quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this year I was suddenly cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:05.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know well now that no one is faster than the Church to turn their back on a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently the authority of the church in the south has been degrading.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:17.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was about time I stop leaving my load on a sinking ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:22.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought to make a profit in the end and move elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:23.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:29.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, while I'm at it, I figured if I can make a big profit off this, I'll go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's time I go on a pilgrimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,would you lend me some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get right to it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you sell your companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:52.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Lonely Smile
